{
  "id": 5080415048171520,
  "name": "Restricting spelling and grammar highlights",
  "summary": "This experiment would change when spelling and grammar hints are applied to text fields to reduce the of websites ability to extract information about the user’s dictionary, specifically:\r\n* Hints would not be applied to a text field that has not had user interaction (an autofocus is insufficient, there must be a click or key press of some kind relative to that field).\r\n* Hints would only be applied once per user interaction (the text cannot be changed programmatically and have hints applied without a click or key press of some kind relative to that field).\r\n",
